Text:
Är detta den sista delen!
Tack bepe86
Nei, dette er ikke siste episode. Episode 5 kom ut i går, men jeg har dessverre ikke fått lastet dn opp enda, men jeg jobber med det.
Could someone please put up Episode 5? If I remember the schedule right, it was aired two days ago...

Addendum: Sorry, I see this has already been discussed; I just didn't pay attention because I'm linguistically challenged. ;)

Whether there won't be any more episodes, or whether the next one is delayed, or whatever is the problem, I'll have to ask the translator.

As episode 5 is here and the translator gave me the gist that bepe won't be uploading 

Raw stream has just finished recording, I am encoding the file at the moment.
